  "texts": [
    "For example, Gemma 2 (Team et al., 2024) is intentionally pretrained on prompts from the LM-SYS benchmark (Zheng et al., 2023).",
    "To study a more modern prompting approach, the experiment in §4 is repeated with two modifications.",
    "First, task-adaptive pretraining is done on prompts-unlabeled texts with instructions for solving the task.",
    "Second, classification training is not performed; train is unused.",
    "The furtherpretrained LLM is immediately prompted to do the task on test."
